# Class Inheritance in JavaScript

```javascript
// Base class
class Animal {
  constructor(name) {
    this.name = name;
  }
  speak() {
    console.log(`${this.name} makes a sound`);
  }
}

// Subclass
class Dog extends Animal {
  speak() {
    console.log(`${this.name} barks`);
  }
}

const d = new Dog('Rex');
d.speak(); // Output: Rex barks
```

